org.afplib.afplib

Interface SEC

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, Triplet
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    SECImpl

    public interface SEC
extends Triplet
    A representation of the model object 'SEC'.

    The following features are supported:

    • RESERVED
    • COLSPCE
    • COLSIZE1
    • COLSIZE2
    • COLSIZE3
    • COLSIZE4
    • COLVALUE

    See Also:
    AfplibPackage.getSEC()
